{"tid":858164,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【重現悲情】天頌苑呎價失守5,000元 高位大跌34%","createTime":"2018-10-11T15:04:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T15:31:36.000Z","uid":174649,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"54466717fad38eb3efd7e2740cd5cdcc9db31329","tid":858164,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T15:04:29.000Z","msg":"股災後，全城二手劈價，天水圍資助房屋成重災區。<br />\n<br />\n祥益地產黃肇雯表示，天水圍居屋天頌苑M座中層15室，實用面積429方呎，今年4月開始於居二市場放盤，最初叫價280萬元，至今累減8口價共70萬元，今日以210萬元售出，呎價4,895元，創屋苑今年新低，與屋苑今年7月高位呎價7,412元比較，大跌34%。<br />\n<br />\n買家為區內客，睇開較為細價的元朗公屋朗屏邨，直至最近，見二手居屋價錢回落，開始物色同區居屋，在施政報告前拉鋸上述單位，客人只肯出價210萬元，業主當時企硬218萬元，直至今天業主同意以210萬元出售。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181011/large/1539269332_3f1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181011%2Flarge%2F1539269332_3f1d.jpg&h=8889df55&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b996045e31e0136687a24f6eada97de04c05309","tid":858164,"uid":83582,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T15:08:36.000Z","msg":"知規矩架啦, 唔計"},{"pid":"f3a48958992011ac1fa01bb1cf50f6c582d6ae04","tid":858164,"uid":40397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T15:10:07.000Z","msg":"係咪08年d 新聞來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f889858899e7642a5b58a6864e00e68268199cd5","tid":858164,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3a48958992011ac1fa01bb1cf50f6c582d6ae04","tid":858164,"uid":40397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T15:10:07.000Z","msg":"係咪08年d 新聞來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T15:10:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181011/58784694\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181011%2F58784694&d=WycYc52